data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!  BRING YOUR OFFERS!  This 3 bedroom, den,  2 bath home is located in the desirable community of Dreaming Summit in Litchfield Park. Complete with new interior paint and the exterior was painted last year. There is a beautiful backyard to relax or entertain your guests in and new Solar that will be paid off at closing!  You will find nearby dining, shopping, schools and the Spring Training facilities of Goodyear and Surprise!
